<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Roleplay Platform!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .feature h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Roleplay Platform!</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  
  <p>We're thrilled to have you on board! You've taken the first step toward enhancing your roleplay experience.</p>
  
  <div class="feature">
    <h3>üöÄ Get Started</h3>
    <p>Complete your profile to help us match you with the perfect roleplay partners and scenarios.</p>
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button" target="_blank">Complete Your Profile</a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="feature">
    <h3>üîç Find Matches</h3>
    <p>Browse through available roleplay scenarios or let our matching algorithm find the perfect partner for you based on your preferences and availability.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="feature">
    <h3>üí¨ Start Roleplaying</h3>
    <p>Use our real-time chat and video features to immerse yourself in your chosen roleplay scenarios.</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reply to this email or check out our <a href="{{helpCenterUrl}}">Help Center</a>.</p>
  
  <p>Happy roleplaying!</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Roleplay Platform Team</p>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>¬© {{currentYear}} Roleplay Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>You're receiving this email because you created an account on Roleplay Platform.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // Add current year to the footer
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
      const yearElements = document.getElementsByClassName('current-year');
      for (let i = 0; i < yearElements.length; i++) {
        yearElements[i].textContent = currentYear;
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
